    },
    "created_at": "2017-03-20T11:30:22Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-20T11:30:22Z",
    "body": "> Why not use sandbox: true if you want native window.open API?\r\n\r\nBecause I also want to use full Node.js support including native addons in the renderer process.\r\nProbably you can proxy it via IPC but I think it would reduce convenience of Electron.\r\n"
  },
