    "created_at": "2017-03-20T11:42:39Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-20T11:42:39Z",
    "body": "Right now sandbox mode supports the `remote` module, so you can probably use most node.js modules without much effort(`require('electron').remote.require('module')`). The `fs` module proxy is already available directly as `require('fs')` from the renderer, but we may add more modules."
  },
