    "created_at": "2017-03-20T12:16:12Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-20T12:20:25Z",
    "body": "I still want to use Node modules directly - using all Node modules through `remote.require` would introduce some problems. For example if you add callbacks to remote objects and reload the window later, you'll have dangling callbacks and Electron will throw errors.\r\n"
  }
